---
// Problem section — three visual "pain" cards
---

<!-- ── Problem ── -->
      <section class="section section--alt" id="problem">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section__eyebrow" data-i18n="problem.eyebrow">Problème</div>
            <h2 data-i18n-html="problem.title">
              Un rendez-vous rapporte.<br /><em>Un compte-rendu coûte.</em>
            </h2>
            <p class="section__lead" data-i18n="problem.lead">
              Les commerciaux terrain passent leurs journées en rendez-vous, pas devant un clavier.
              Les informations clés restent dans la tête et s'évaporent avant même le retour au
              bureau.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="prob-grid">
            <!-- Card 1 — time lost -->
            <article class="prob-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
              <div class="prob-viz prob-viz--time">
                <div class="prob-viz__top">
                  <span class="prob-moon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z" /></svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="prob-time">21:47</span>
                </div>
                <div class="prob-bignum">45<span>min</span></div>
                <div class="prob-bar" aria-hidden="true"><span></span></div>
                <div class="prob-bar__legend">
                  <span data-i18n="problem.viz1.legend">Reporting au lieu de vendre</span>
                  <span class="prob-warn" data-i18n="problem.viz1.perday">+1 h / jour</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 data-i18n="problem.card1.title">45 minutes perdues par RDV</h3>
              <p data-i18n="problem.card1.text">
                Rédiger un compte-rendu après chaque réunion, en voiture ou le soir. Chaque
                commercial y passe plus d'une heure par jour, sans générer aucun chiffre
                d'affaires.
              </p>
            </article>

            <!-- Card 2 — forgotten commitments -->
            <article class="prob-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
              <div class="prob-viz prob-viz--fade">
                <span class="prob-tag" style="--o:1;--y:0" data-i18n="problem.viz2.t1">Promesse client</span>
                <span class="prob-tag" style="--o:.62;--y:-2px" data-i18n="problem.viz2.t2">Objection clé</span>
                <span class="prob-tag" style="--o:.3;--y:-4px" data-i18n="problem.viz2.t3">Opportunité détectée</span>
                <span class="prob-tag prob-tag--gone" aria-hidden="true">· · ·</span>
              </div>
              <h3 data-i18n="problem.card2.title">Engagements oubliés</h3>
              <p data-i18n="problem.card2.text">
                Ce qui n'est pas écrit dans la foulée disparaît. Les promesses clients, les
                objections clés, les opportunités détectées : tout s'évapore avant la prochaine
                réunion d'équipe.
              </p>
            </article>

            <!-- Card 3 — blind manager -->
            <article class="prob-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
              <div class="prob-viz prob-viz--blind">
                <div class="prob-dash">
                  <div class="prob-dash__bar">
                    <i></i><i></i><i></i>
                    <span data-i18n="problem.viz3.team">Activité de l'équipe</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="prob-dash__rows" aria-hidden="true">
                    <span class="prob-dash__row" style="width:92%"></span>
                    <span class="prob-dash__row" style="width:78%"></span>
                    <span class="prob-dash__row" style="width:85%"></span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="prob-dash__q" aria-hidden="true">?</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 data-i18n="problem.card3.title">Manager aveugle</h3>
              <p data-i18n="problem.card3.text">
                Le responsable ne voit pas ce qui se passe sur le terrain tant que le commercial ne
                rapporte pas. Et ça arrive trop tard pour agir sur les opportunités ou les risques.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <style>
          .prob-grid {
            margin-top: 46px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
          }
          .prob-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

          .prob-viz {
            position: relative;
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 18px;
            min-height: 158px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
          }
          .prob-viz::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0 0 auto 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(240, 180, 41, 0.55), transparent);
          }

          /* Card 1 — time */
          .prob-viz--time { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
          .prob-viz__top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; color: #f0b429; }
          .prob-moon svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }
          .prob-time { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
          .prob-bignum { font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 800; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1; color: var(--text); margin: 10px 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
          .prob-bignum span { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 5px; letter-spacing: 0; }
          .prob-bar { height: 8px; border-radius: 5px; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; }
          .prob-bar span { display: block; height: 100%; width: 82%; border-radius: 5px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(240, 180, 41, 0.45), #f0b429); animation: prob-fill 1.4s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both; }
          .prob-bar__legend { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px; margin-top: 9px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
          .prob-warn { color: #f0b429; }

          /* Card 2 — evaporating info */
          .prob-viz--fade { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 9px; justify-content: center; }
          .prob-tag { align-self: flex-start; padding: 7px 12px; border-radius: 9px; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text); opacity: var(--o); transform: translateY(var(--y)); animation: prob-evap 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
          .prob-tag:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
          .prob-tag:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
          .prob-tag--gone { opacity: 0.22; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: var(--muted); border-style: dashed; animation: none; }

          /* Card 3 — blind dashboard */
          .prob-viz--blind { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
          .prob-dash { position: relative; width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 11px; background: var(--surface2); overflow: hidden; }
          .prob-dash__bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; padding: 8px 11px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12); }
          .prob-dash__bar i { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); }
          .prob-dash__bar span { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.56rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 4px; }
          .prob-dash__rows { padding: 14px 13px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 11px; filter: blur(3.5px); opacity: 0.6; }
          .prob-dash__row { height: 12px; border-radius: 5px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border), transparent); }
          .prob-dash__q { position: absolute; inset: 26px 0 0 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 800; font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.85; }

          /* shared title/text */
          .prob-card h3 { font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.3; margin: 20px 0 8px; }
          .prob-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

          @keyframes prob-fill { from { width: 0; } to { width: 82%; } }
          @keyframes prob-evap { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(var(--y)); } 50% { transform: translateY(calc(var(--y) - 4px)); opacity: calc(var(--o) * 0.7); } }

          @media (max-width: 880px) {
            .prob-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
          }
          @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            .prob-bar span, .prob-tag { animation: none; }
          }
        </style>
      </section>
